def visit_else(self, node, else_name=None):
    """ID: 9412cf58-6ed6-436d-850d-78bc044a9d2e"""
    self.name_stack.append(else_name)
    self.method_stack.append(else_name)
    for stmt in node.orelse:
        self.visit(stmt)
    self.method_stack.pop()
    self.name_stack.pop()
